
Users
    email       =   Varchar(100)    = primary_key
    name        =   Varchar(50)
    profile     =   Varchar(200)
    remove      =   Int(1)
    timestamp   =   timestamp

Todos
    todo_id     =   Int(10)         = primary_key
    email       =   Varchar(100)    = foreign_key
    text        =   Varchar(500)
    completed   =   Int(1)
    removed     =   Int(1)
    timestamp   =   timestamp